This template displays an external link to a page for a game at the [[BoardGameGeek]] website.

== Usage ==
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>|<var>ID3</var>|<var>NAME3</var>}}

Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>|name{{=}}<var>NAME</var>}}

== Examples ==

=== Single link ===
''Usage in the article {{tsl|en|Castle Risk||Castle Risk}}, with article name as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|2557}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}2557}}

''Usage with name parameter as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|2557|Castle Risk}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id{{=}}2557|name{{=}}Castle Risk}}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|2557|Castle Risk}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|id=2557|name=Castle Risk}}

''URLs:''
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/2557 https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/{{hilite|2557}}]</kbd> (used in template)
: <kbd>[https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/2557/castle-risk https://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/{{hilite|2557}}/castle-risk]</kbd> (redirect at website)

=== Multiple links ===
''Usage:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|54|Tikal|855|Java}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|54|Tikal|855|Java|2955|Mexica}}

''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|54|Tikal|855|Java}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|54|Tikal|855|Java|2955|Mexica}}

